Package org.team1540.rooster.testers.motor

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BurnoutTester
    Reports motor burnouts by comparing the current draw across a series of similarly-purposed motors and reporting low outliers or checking if a single motor is below the cutoff.
    ControllersMultiTester
    Simple automated testing for motors.
    EncoderTester
    Reports if an encoder appears to be non-functional by checking to see if a motor is running and if the corresponding encoder is moving.
    SimpleControllersTester
    A simple command for testing a series of IMotorControllers.
